_header: Lou lou lou where he goes
Note: Written twice, under each musical part.
_description: A two-part song, inserted in a Latin grammatical text — three lines

Lou lou lou wer e gozA lou lou lou were gozfor hyr iles myn
                    aly[w]ater ter ter lou
